      <title>澳大利亚西太平洋银行任命新首席执行官，摆脱治理危机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/westpac-appoints-new-chief-executive-officer-2024-09-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西太平洋银行（Westpac）是澳大利亚第二大抵押贷款机构，该银行将其商业和财富部门主管提升为首席执行官，并誓言要利用改进后的治理结构扩大其商业贷款业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/westpac-appoints-new-chief-executive-officer-2024-09-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 21:42:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
